WEBVTT

00:01.335 --> 00:03.871
Free the innocent.
Find the guilty.

00:03.904 --> 00:06.716
- Are you sure you want to poke the bear?
- I want to rip his heart out.

00:06.740 --> 00:09.710
All-new episodes
of Proven Innocent Fridays.

00:09.743 --> 00:11.545
And check out
our other hit shows...

00:11.579 --> 00:14.282
The Resident, 9-1-1, and Empire.

00:14.382 --> 00:15.916
Only on Fox.

00:17.017 --> 00:19.019
Previously on Proven Innocent...

00:19.053 --> 00:20.097
Madeline Scott,
you are under arrest

00:20.121 --> 00:21.922
for the murder
of Rosemary Lynch.

00:21.955 --> 00:23.833
If you can connect this lantern
to Madeline Scott,

00:23.857 --> 00:25.493
you'll win by a landslide.

00:25.526 --> 00:26.994
Ravi was possibly a murderer.

00:27.027 --> 00:29.663
After Rosemary's death,
all evidence vanishes.

00:29.697 --> 00:31.175
Only supporting the theory
that he's dead.

00:31.199 --> 00:33.334
Sarah, I know
this is a lot to ask.

00:33.367 --> 00:35.879
- We're hoping you'll testify to all of this.
- Glad I can finally help.

00:35.903 --> 00:38.005
- Linda, I need you to testify.
- I'll testify.

00:38.038 --> 00:40.117
You shouldn't have let my
sister get anywhere near him.

00:40.141 --> 00:42.410
I think I deserve to see my son.

00:42.443 --> 00:44.678
- He's got nothing.
- I've got everything.

00:44.712 --> 00:46.480
I've got Levi.

00:53.087 --> 00:55.055
We are now 100% sure we have

00:55.089 --> 00:56.890
the weapon Madeline Scott used

00:56.924 --> 00:58.192
to murder Rosemary Lynch.

00:58.226 --> 00:59.793
Justice...

00:59.827 --> 01:01.962
will finally be served.

01:04.565 --> 01:06.567
What do you fear most?

01:07.568 --> 01:09.370
For those wrongfully accused,

01:09.403 --> 01:12.873
their biggest fear
is hearing the word "guilty."

01:12.906 --> 01:15.743
That one simple word

01:15.776 --> 01:17.645
can take away
your precious freedom

01:17.678 --> 01:21.382
and condemn you to prison
for the rest of your life.

01:21.415 --> 01:23.083
On this week's episode

01:23.117 --> 01:24.885
of Until Proven Innocent,
we'll discuss

01:24.918 --> 01:27.888
what happens when that fear
hits close to home.

01:27.921 --> 01:30.424
When the freedom
at stake belongs

01:30.458 --> 01:31.759
to someone you love.

01:31.792 --> 01:34.094
Madeline Scott is on trial

01:34.128 --> 01:36.897
for the murder of Rosemary Lynch

01:36.930 --> 01:38.832
and she is an innocent woman.

01:38.866 --> 01:42.403
So, my coworkers and I
have been transformed

01:42.436 --> 01:44.905
from legal advocates
to those suffering

01:44.938 --> 01:46.940
right alongside
the wrongfully accused.

01:46.974 --> 01:49.477
And we will continue fighting

01:49.510 --> 01:51.579
with every ounce
of strength that we have

01:51.612 --> 01:54.748
because we have seen how,
in an instant,

01:54.782 --> 01:56.350
your freedom can vanish.

01:56.384 --> 01:57.685
And I know

01:57.718 --> 01:59.853
that in the depths of my soul,

01:59.887 --> 02:02.790
I would be lost
without Madeline Scott, so...

02:04.158 --> 02:06.760
I am scared to death
of losing my best friend.

02:08.795 --> 02:10.130
How'd it go with Sarah?

02:10.163 --> 02:12.366
I need to review
the cult timeline with her.

02:12.400 --> 02:13.801
- How about Linda?
- Well, she's got

02:13.834 --> 02:16.136
some interesting details
on this Ravi character.

02:16.170 --> 02:18.606
Aka Robert Carter,
deceased con man,

02:18.639 --> 02:21.609
cult leader and, serial rapist.

02:21.642 --> 02:24.212
And our best option
for an alternative suspect.

02:24.245 --> 02:26.680
We may not even
have to present a case.

02:26.714 --> 02:29.283
We might be able
to knock out Bellows' case

02:29.317 --> 02:31.118
on lack of sufficient evidence.

02:31.151 --> 02:33.297
- You really believe that?
- Well, it's not impossible.

02:33.321 --> 02:34.622
What does Bellows really have?

02:34.655 --> 02:37.024
A lantern with no hair, fibers,

02:37.057 --> 02:39.627
fingerprints...
unreliable witnesses.

02:39.660 --> 02:41.462
Heather "Bitch" Husband.

02:41.495 --> 02:44.298
Who I'll decimate on cross.
I got this.

02:44.332 --> 02:46.033
What do we do about Levi?

02:46.066 --> 02:48.636
Bellows has had him alone
and incommunicado for a week.

02:48.669 --> 02:50.404
What if he got to him?

02:50.438 --> 02:52.139
What if he threatened him
and he flipped?

02:52.172 --> 02:53.650
You really think
your own brother's gonna lie

02:53.674 --> 02:55.042
to implicate you for murder?

02:55.075 --> 02:56.977
Hey, either Levi
tells the truth and testifies

02:57.010 --> 02:58.812
you didn't do it,
or I'll expose his lies

02:58.846 --> 03:00.881
and go after Bellows
for suborning perjury.

03:02.216 --> 03:03.251
We're ready.

03:05.519 --> 03:08.155
What do you think
Levi's gonna say?

03:08.188 --> 03:11.492
I have absolutely no idea.

03:11.525 --> 03:14.428
Day one of the retrial
of Madeline Scott,

03:14.462 --> 03:17.698
only this time she's being tried
without her brother Levi,

03:17.731 --> 03:19.567
who some say has
turned against his sister

03:19.600 --> 03:22.403
as the prosecution's
star witness.

03:22.436 --> 03:25.573
Madeline,
how does it feel to know

03:25.606 --> 03:27.851
- that your own brother has betrayed you?
- How does it feel

03:27.875 --> 03:29.919
- to be a two-faced, lying hag?
- We have no comment.

03:29.943 --> 03:31.955
Getting scared now that a guilty
verdict is finally on the way?

03:31.979 --> 03:33.957
You know... Do you have any idea
how much damage you do

03:33.981 --> 03:36.083
with your hyped-up coverage
and sensationalism?

03:36.116 --> 03:38.386
This is an actual life
that you are destroying

03:38.419 --> 03:40.954
for an extra half-point
of ratings on a crappy show.

03:40.988 --> 03:42.923
All right, like I said,
we have no comment.

03:42.956 --> 03:46.193
Madeline Scott,
clearly under pressure.

03:46.226 --> 03:49.763
Entering the courtroom now is
State's Attorney Gore Bellows.

03:49.797 --> 03:51.941
- Mr. Bellows.
- Don't have anything for you right now, Susan.

03:51.965 --> 03:53.534
Gore...

03:53.567 --> 03:54.835
get her.

